        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4402",
        "content": "In vain he roared, and invoked fair Dulcinea del Toboso: for frogs' wild croaking seemed more loud, more sonorous than all his invocations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
